白與事實相符，被告罪嫌堪予認定。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e5%98%89%e7%b0%a1%2c289%2c20220411%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,嘉簡,289,20220411,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉簡","JNO":"289","JDATE":"20220411","JTITLE":"毀棄損壞"}